                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "The golden path baseline is non-negotiable: structured JSON logging, OTel traces, Prometheus metrics, and security controls are wired up by the scaffold and enforced by CI gates."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Log records must include "
